title: Kali linux 1.0.4/ i386 gnome 32bit Gnome VM
description:
The most advanced and versatile penetration testing distribution ever created.

This is the version that is to be ran by a virtual machine. I personally recommend VMware and virtual Box.

After downloading the file, use WinRaR or 7-Zip to extract files.

Make sure to install the vitalization application of you chose.

After vitalization application is installed, double click kali-linux-i386-gnome-vm.vmx and your all set.
